#: index.docbook:417
msgid ""
"Besides the options available on the <link linkend=\"config-general\"> "
"<guilabel>General</guilabel></link> tab, there are even more ways to "
"customize &knewsticker; to fit your needs available on the <guilabel>News "
"sources</guilabel> tab. This page mainly consists of a table which lets you "
"manage and maintain the list of news sites &knewsticker; queries for news. "
"Click on any entry with the right mouse button to open a context menu which "
"lets you remove the current entry, or add a new entry with the properties of "
"the selected entry."
